FBIS3-52591 "drnes004_n_94003" FBIS-NES-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 LEBANON Iranian Envoy Criticizes Vatican Move on Israel NC0501175194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 5 Jan 94 NC0501175194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Yext] Iranian Ambassador in Lebanon Homayun 'Alizadeh has attacked what he called international attempts to legitimize the Zionist enemy and noted the Vatican's efforts in this respect. He said this was bad and wrong both tactically and strategically. The Iranian ambassador made these remarks after visiting acting Mufti Shaykh Muhammad Rashid Qabbani.
